extendedInfo.description: If you want to lead a healthy lifestyle than you owe it to yourself and your family to explore the possibilities of the alternative medicine called Naturopathy... And this App is a great way to start exploring. Naturopathic Medicine is the best of ancient, traditional practices combined with recent evidence from cutting edge technical research. This Apps has videos that are an introduction to what Naturopathy is and a page that describes Alternative Medicine. I've also put in some videos about Healing Herbs, a Pictures section to know what healthy herbs look like, a news feed from a world-renowned Naturopathic institution, a Healthy Massage video page and a basic Yoga page.If you are looking for a single place to get started on the road to natural health and feeling better, download this Free App now!

reviews.title: very inaccurate applications
reviews.comment: this application claims that naturopathic medicine is not based on scientific findings. that is completely untrue.
reviews.author: A Google User
